      "notes": "Ashes of Holloway Bay is a mature narrative mystery investigation game that deals with the realistic aftermath of a fatal house fire in which three people lost their lives.\r\n\r\nThe game contains references to death, smoke inhalation, and a deliberate arson incident. These themes are presented through official police reports, post-mortem documents, news footage, witness interviews, and digital evidence, all in a documentary-style case-file interface.\r\n\r\nThere is no graphic violence, blood, gore, sexual content, or nudity. The tone is dark and atmospheric, focusing on investigation, evidence analysis, and logical deduction rather than sensationalism.\r\n\r\nPlayers should be comfortable with themes of loss, tragedy, and criminal investigation. The game is intended for a mature audience interested in realistic detective storytelling."
